    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26b.24"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">24</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        Maxwell, Nebr.
                        Aug. 4, 1958
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>The Nebraska Writers Guild Board held its meeting Saturday, August 2, and unanimously voted to invite you to be our luncheon speaker for the annual Fall Meeting at the Town House in Omaha on September 13.</p>
                
                <p>Will you please send a picture of yourself and all pertinent data necessary for the "Who's Who" department of the Guild Bulletin to Mrs. John <hi rend="caps">B.</hi> Otte, 3124 No. 58th St., Omaha 4, Nebr? This is for the program pages, you understand, and as you are the featured speaker of the day we like quite a colorful and complete resume of your activities. The editors are now in the process of making up the Bulletin and would appreciate this information as soon as you can possibly get it into their hands.</p>
                
                <p>You will receive your copy of the Bulletin containing the complete program about September 1. If there is anything else you wish to know about the meeting please write to me about it. We are most happy over the prospect of having you at our meeting.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Sincerely,</salute>
                
                    <signed>Mrs. Harry Yost</signed>
                
                    <signed>Mrs. Harry Yost
                
                    Secretary-treasurer - Nebr. Writers Guild</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <postscript>
                    <p>Will you please send Mrs. Otte the title of your address, also. That is very important and I almost forgot to mention it.</p>
          
                    <closer>
                        <salute>Thank you.</salute>
                        
                        <signed>N.Y.</signed>
                    </closer>
                </postscript>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
